Data.name: MPTTestPlan FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in (MILES4ALL-9756)

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllButPASS FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', 'TODO|EXECUTING|FAIL|ABORTED|BLOCKED') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODO FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', TODO) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODOUnassigned FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', TODO, __NULL__) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanFAIL FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', FAIL) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanNoEvidence FNC BE
Data.description: All Tests in FNC BE Test Plan without Test Evidence
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND ((issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'false', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'false', 'false')))

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlan FNC BE

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanFFlag1Open FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND Labels in (eSignature) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanFFlag1OpenCritical FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND Labels in (eSignature) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = Critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanNonMiles FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND component is not EMPTY AND component != MRI ORDER BY rank

Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRegression FNC BE') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanRegressionOpenCritical FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRegression FNC BE') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = Critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanRemainingOpenCritical FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRemaining FNC BE') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND (labels not in (eSignature) OR labels is EMPTY) AND Status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = Critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser FNC BE
Data.description: Executions in Test Plan for current user
Data.jql: filter=270731 AND issue in testExecWithTestRunsAssignedToUser() ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanPASSNoEvidence FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('MPTTestsInTestPlanPASSNoEvidence FNC BE') AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('MPTTestPlan FNC BE')
